Read Nightingale Data (format 1)

read_nightingale.Rd

Read Nightingale Data (format 1)

Usage

read_nightingale(filepath)

Arguments

filepath

character, commercial Nightingale excel sheet with extension .xls or .xlsx

Value

list, list(data = 3D matrix, samples = samples data.table, features = features data.table)

Examples

# version 1 data format
filepath1 <- system.file("extdata", "nightingale_v1_example.xlsx", package = "metaboprep")
read_nightingale(filepath1)
